  artworkTitle: "The Thinker",
  artworkCredit: "Auguste Rodin, 1904",
  artworkCaption:
    "Rodin's brooding figure — humanity bent under the weight of thought, unable to escape the shadow of the moral revolution Christianity wrought.",
